version_description: The voicings of the chords have been modified to add extra feeling to the song, and uniqueness to each part.
Coldplay - Warning Sign Acoustic version (AOL live session 2003).
All of the 5 star versions of these songs were either not fully completed (Not every verse/ chorus had the chords) and some were done with the wrong Capo which made for the wrong chords too
The song is not played with a capo and has non-standard tuning.
